  "detailed_description": "<h1>WISHLIST NOW AND GET NOTIFIED WHEN AT TONY'S RELEASES</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2741490/extras/ef0dcd45bf41e034243005a2e364a55b.poster.avif?t=1716050815\" width=736 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2741490/extras/ef0dcd45bf41e034243005a2e364a55b.webm?t=1716050815\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2741490/extras/ef0dcd45bf41e034243005a2e364a55b.mp4?t=1716050815\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>At Tony's is a first-person horror experience taking place in a haunted pizzeria.<br>The last night shift worker <strong>vanished mysteriously</strong>, it's your turn to step in to help the family's business.<br><br><strong>Will you survive your shift, cooking pizzas while unveiling the restaurant's mysteries?</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2741490/extras/4aa4c1fab311636e18eb0232da07b2b3.poster.avif?t=1716050815\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2741490/extras/4aa4c1fab311636e18eb0232da07b2b3.webm?t=1716050815\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2741490/extras/4aa4c1fab311636e18eb0232da07b2b3.mp4?t=1716050815\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Immersive Story</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Hand-crafted environments with secrets to uncover<br></li><li> Story told through voice messages and mysterious notes<br></li><li> Discover the secret behind the haunted pizzeria</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2741490/extras/da9bf40948e77583232596383827d775.poster.avif?t=1716050815\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2741490/extras/da9bf40948e77583232596383827d775.webm?t=1716050815\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"> <li> Atmospheric environment and photo-realistic graphics.<br></li><li> game loop combining elements from classic horror games.<br></li><li> Compelling story with multiple endings<br></li><li> Unpredictable A.I. and scares</li></ul>",
